  "title": "An Old Score with Solo",
  "summary": "A New Republic recon flight from Falcon Squadron, joined by Han Solo and Chewbacca in the Millennium Falcon, drops out of hyperspace over Imperial-held Corellia and is intercepted by fighters led by the veteran Imperial pilot Danik Kreldin in his Scimitar. In the swirling dogfight, rookie pilots Andra and Kieran Tain take heavy fire from Kreldin while Han doggedly pursues the Imperial ace. The arrival of Captain Mora Rodriga in a borrowed Mantaray turns personal: Mora, consumed by grief and rage over the comrades and the love Kreldin's past atrocities cost him, confronts his nemesis but breaks off to rescue the gravely wounded Kieran instead. Kreldin and his wingman Grymm Selcan ultimately knock out a crippled A-wing and salvage its pilot, while the battered survivors of Falcon Squadron pull out of the recon-gone-wrong.",
